22
00:04:13,211 --> 00:04:16,214
...one airing, $850, but you're in luck.

23
00:04:16,381 --> 00:04:18,967
Today, we have a one-time special.

24
00:04:19,133 --> 00:04:22,971
Our elite package:
seven commercials, seven airings...

25
00:04:23,137 --> 00:04:25,556
...for forty--

26
00:04:25,932 --> 00:04:29,227
Forty-six hundred dollars.

27
00:04:29,394 --> 00:04:31,104
Yeah, $4,600.

28
00:04:31,271 --> 00:04:33,648
And we can add-- Hello?

29
