...because you keep putting me on hold.

32
00:04:49,622 --> 00:04:50,832
Okay, my sit--

33
00:04:50,999 --> 00:04:53,793
Hello? My sit--
Yes. My situation is this. I--

34
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:56,337
