for the next 12 months.

37
00:05:04,387 --> 00:05:05,763
Yes. Suspended.

38
00:05:05,930 --> 00:05:10,852
So I'm not practicing,
so I don't need malpractice insurance.

39
00:05:11,019 --> 00:05:13,396
And I'd like to speak to someone
about a refund.

40
00:05:14,981 --> 00:05:19,444
What--? Yeah-- Well, then, may I please
speak to someone who can make a decision?

41
00:05:19,610 --> 00:05:22,113
No, no. Don't put me on hold again.
Please. Hell--?

42
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:24,365
Hello? Hell--?

43
00:05:26,034 --> 00:05:27,368
[CAR HORN BLARING]

44
00:05:30,747 --> 00:05:32,957
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

45
00:05:50,099 --> 00:05:52,685
