54
00:06:11,537 --> 00:06:13,164
No phones allowed in jail.

55
00:06:13,331 --> 00:06:15,541
Well, hold on there, buddy.

56
00:06:15,708 --> 00:06:17,794
I mean, who do you think you are, huh?

57
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:20,254
You--? You think you can treat us like this?

58
00:06:20,421 --> 00:06:23,633
We're out here for the good
of the great city of Albuquerque.

59
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:26,511
Not for you. You're not our lord and master.

60
00:06:26,677 --> 00:06:30,765
You don't get to sit back
and decide who's worthy and who isn't.

61
00:06:30,932 --> 00:06:32,183
Am I right?

62
00:06:33,392 --> 00:06:36,312
Dude, are you gonna get in the van or what?

63
00:06:38,856 --> 00:06:42,193
Come on. Thirty minutes, that's not right.
You can do better than that.

64
00:06:44,695 --> 00:06:46,280
